    <briefdescription>
<para>This file holds helper functions to work with our own trace user data handling. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It works by storing the trace user data in one wave per graph. It is cleaned up when the graph is killed. For subwindows the window hook responsible for cleaning up is attached to the top-most parent as only that is receiving window hook events. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
